body_html:
Hello @nectario .
Good to hear that cmake works!
I dont know where the cmake build put the dlls but for bazel, it is under tensorflow/lib_package if everything is successful.

It is probably called libtensorflow_jni.so. You might want to look for it in the build folder...

body:
Hello @nectario .
Good to hear that cmake works! 
I dont know where the cmake build put the dlls but for bazel, it is under tensorflow/lib_package if everything is successful. 

It is probably called libtensorflow_jni.so. You might want to look for it in the build folder...
